text: The New Right (, HaYamin HeHadash) is a right-wing political party in Israel, established in December 2018 by justice minister Ayelet Shaked and education minister Naftali Bennett. Participating in the Bennett-Lapid Government. ==References== Category:Political parties in Israel Category:Zionist parties Category:2010s establishments in Israel Category:2018 establishments in Asia
